1
00:00:19,666 --> 00:00:22,916
- ( humming )

2
00:00:23,000 --> 00:00:26,125
- THESE CREPES ARE HARD TO GET.
THEY ONLY MAKE TEN A DAY.

3
00:00:26,208 --> 00:00:27,791
