5
00:00:32,458 --> 00:00:34,333
- THAT HURT.
- OW.

6
00:00:34,416 --> 00:00:36,291
- HEY, COME ON, WE GOT TO GO.
- DON'T MOVE.

7
00:00:36,375 --> 00:00:37,375
- ( gasps )

8
00:00:39,125 --> 00:00:41,625
- CATCH YOU LATER, ALLIGATOR.
- HEY, COME BACK HERE.

9
00:00:41,708 --> 00:00:42,916
- OH, NO, WHERE'S MY CREPE?

10
00:00:45,416 --> 00:00:47,291
HAPPINESS ENERGY
IS STILL WORKING.

11
00:00:52,083 --> 00:00:54,083
- YEAH, WHAT?
- DROP THE ATTITUDE, MISS.

12
00:00:54,166 --> 00:00:56,791
- SHOPLIFTER.
- SHOPLIFTER?

13
00:00:58,208 --> 00:01:00,458
- I'M GONNA HAVE
TO TAKE YOU DOWNTOWN.

14
00:01:00,541 --> 00:01:03,250
- HUH? YOU'RE KIDDING ME.

15
00:01:03,333 --> 00:01:05,083
YOU'RE GONNA RUIN MY
HAPPY MOMENT RIGHT NOW,

16
00:01:05,166 --> 00:01:06,791
AND I DIDN'T EVEN DO ANYTHING.

17
00:01:06,875 --> 00:01:09,375
- CALM DOWN OR I'M GONNA HAVE TO
BOOK YOU FOR RESISTING ARREST.

18
00:01:09,458 --> 00:01:11,416
- YOU STUPID JERK.
- Ranmaru: HOLD ON.

19
00:01:13,333 --> 00:01:16,000
- BEFORE YOU GO AROUND
PREACHING ABOUT HAPPINESS,

20
00:01:16,083 --> 00:01:18,791
IT MIGHT DO YOU SOME GOOD
TO TAKE A LOOK IN THE MIRROR.

21
00:01:18,875 --> 00:01:21,208
GIRLS SHOULD NEVER RAISE
THEIR FISTS IN ANGER.

22
00:01:22,541 --> 00:01:25,083
ESPECIALLY IF HAPPINESS
IS WHAT THEY'RE AFTER.

23
00:01:26,458 --> 00:01:29,708
WHERE ANGER THRIVES,
HAPPINESS IS ABSENT,

24
00:01:29,791 --> 00:01:31,125
I GUESS NOBODY
EVER TOOK THE TIME

25
00:01:31,208 --> 00:01:34,250
TO TEACH YOU THAT, LITTLE GIRL.

26
00:01:34,333 --> 00:01:35,375
- WHAT?

27
00:03:09,041 --> 00:03:11,291
- WHO'S THAT?
- SHE ISN'T YOUR FRIEND?

28
00:03:11,375 --> 00:03:13,666
- NO, I DON'T KNOW
THAT GIRL, I SWEAR...

29
00:03:15,666 --> 00:03:20,375
IT WAS ME, OFFICERS, I CONFESS.
IT'S TRUE, I SHOPLIFTED.

30
00:03:20,458 --> 00:03:21,916
- BUT NOT BECAUSE I WANTED TO,

31
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:24,416
I TOLD HER NO BUT SHE
WOULDN'T LISTEN.

32
00:03:24,500 --> 00:03:27,583
SHE SAID SHE'D HURT ME IF I
DIDN'T DO WHAT SHE ORDERED.

33
00:03:27,666 --> 00:03:29,666
- HMM.
- DID YOU PUT HER UP TO THIS?

34
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:32,291
- THAT'S LOW.
- WAIT, YOU CAN'T BE SERIOUS.

35
00:03:32,375 --> 00:03:36,125
- ARREST HER RIGHT NOW.
- ( screams )

36
00:03:36,208 --> 00:03:38,583
- WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO ASK YOU
A COUPLE OF QUESTIONS, MISS.

37
00:03:38,666 --> 00:03:40,625
HEY, WHERE'D SHE GO?

38
00:03:40,708 --> 00:03:45,666
- DAMN, I'LL MAKE HER PAY.
I'LL TEACH HER TO MESS WITH ME.

39
00:03:46,291 --> 00:03:47,333
- DELISH.

40
00:03:54,958 --> 00:03:57,625
- I WONDER WHAT HAPPENED
TO THAT GIRL I GOT INTO IT WITH.

41
00:03:57,708 --> 00:03:59,333
I BET SHE WAS SUPER PISSED,

42
00:03:59,416 --> 00:04:01,833
OH, WELL. IT'S NOT LIKE
I'LL EVER SEE HER AGAIN.

43
00:04:01,916 --> 00:04:03,958
- ALL RIGHT. THERE'S A
NEW TRANSFER STUDENT

44
00:04:04,041 --> 00:04:05,958
I'D LIKE TO INTRODUCE
YOU TO TODAY.

45
00:04:06,041 --> 00:04:09,541
- EXCUSE ME, WHY IS IT WE ALWAYS
HAVE NEW TRANSFER STUDENTS?

46
00:04:09,625 --> 00:04:11,125
- GOOD QUESTION,

47
00:04:11,208 --> 00:04:13,750
IT'S BECAUSE THE MAIN CHARACTER
OF OUR ANIME IS IN THIS CLASS.

48
00:04:13,833 --> 00:04:16,416
- THAT MAKES SENSE.
- ALL RIGHT, SON. COME ON IN.

49
00:04:20,708 --> 00:04:22,375
- ( exclaims )

50
00:04:22,458 --> 00:04:25,625
- MISTER RINDO, YOU PREFER TO BE
CALLED RANMARU, IS THAT RIGHT?

51
00:04:25,708 --> 00:04:30,125
- UH, IT'S MISS RINDO, BUT YEAH,
I PREFER TO BE CALLED RANMARU.

52
00:04:30,208 --> 00:04:32,375
I LOVE KARATE, MY
DREAM IS TO BRING BACK

53
00:04:32,458 --> 00:04:33,958
MY FATHER'S MARTIAL ARTS DOJO,

54
00:04:34,041 --> 00:04:36,041
THAT CLOSED DOWN
AFTER HE WENT BANKRUPT.

55
00:04:36,125 --> 00:04:40,583
- I SEE, IS THIS A SO CALLED
BOY RAISED AS A GIRL PATTERN?

56
00:04:40,666 --> 00:04:42,791
- STOP CALLING ME A
BOY, DOUCHE- BAG,

57
00:04:42,875 --> 00:04:45,166
I MEAN, UNLESS YOU WANT YOUR
FACE BASHED IN.

58
00:04:45,250 --> 00:04:46,625
- SORRY.

59
00:04:46,708 --> 00:04:48,458
- OH, THIS IS NOT GOOD.

60
00:04:48,541 --> 00:04:50,666
THERE'S NO POSSIBLE WAY THIS
GIRL DOESN'T REMEMBER ME,

61
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:52,250
IS THERE?

62
00:04:52,333 --> 00:04:55,708
WAIT, I'VE GOT IT. I KNOW A WAY
OUT OF THIS, I NEED A DISGUISE.

63
00:04:57,166 --> 00:04:59,458
SHE'LL NEVER RECOGNIZE ME NOW.

64
00:05:02,291 --> 00:05:04,541
- ( chuckles ) IF THIS IS A
COSPLAY CONTEST, YOU'RE TOAST.

65
00:05:04,625 --> 00:05:06,375
- THIS HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH YOU, POVERTY GOD.

66
00:05:06,458 --> 00:05:08,166
YOU'RE JUST DRAWING
ATTENTION TO US.

67
00:05:08,250 --> 00:05:11,083
- SWEET. I WANT IN ON THIS.

68
00:05:11,166 --> 00:05:13,250
- COME ON, NOT YOU TOO.

69
00:05:13,333 --> 00:05:15,708
- TAKE A SEAT IN THE BACK ROW
NEXT TO THE HALLWAY, PLEASE.

70
00:05:15,791 --> 00:05:16,791
- KAY- O.

71
00:05:20,375 --> 00:05:22,791
- SOMETHING IS NOT RIGHT
OVER HERE. HMM?

72
00:05:22,875 --> 00:05:24,666
HEY, YOU'RE THE GIRL
FROM YESTERDAY.

73
00:05:24,750 --> 00:05:27,458
- THIS SUCKS. SHE TOOK
ONE LOOK AND FIGURED IT OUT.

74
00:05:27,541 --> 00:05:29,000
- WE NEED TO TALK.

75
00:05:30,208 --> 00:05:32,208
- SHE'S GONNA MURDER ME.
- HUH?

76
00:05:32,291 --> 00:05:34,125
- MISS ICHIKO,
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

77
00:05:34,208 --> 00:05:36,916
- THE TRANSFER STUDENT GOT
VIOLENT WITH ME OUT OF NOWHERE.

78
00:05:37,000 --> 00:05:38,041
- HUH?

79
00:05:38,125 --> 00:05:39,500
- WHY WOULD YOU DO
SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

80
00:05:39,583 --> 00:05:41,666
- WE WON'T STAND FOR
THAT TYPE OF BEHAVIOR, NEWB.

81
00:05:41,750 --> 00:05:44,250
- YEAH, NOT COOL.
- YOU GOT THE WRONG IDEA HERE.

82
00:05:44,333 --> 00:05:45,791
- ( smirks )

83
00:05:45,875 --> 00:05:49,166
- ( grunts ) DAMN YOU.

84
00:05:50,458 --> 00:05:52,583
- I'LL MAKE HER PAY.

85
00:05:52,666 --> 00:05:54,666
BUT THERE'S NO WAY I CAN
GET TO HER AT SCHOOL,

86
00:05:54,750 --> 00:05:56,750
NOT WITH HER IDIOT
BRIGADE AROUND.

87
00:05:56,833 --> 00:05:58,375
- HMM?
- ( chuckles )

88
00:05:59,458 --> 00:06:01,208
- ( door bell rings )

89
00:06:01,291 --> 00:06:02,333
- Ichiko: COMING!

90
00:06:06,583 --> 00:06:09,875
THIS SO ISN'T HAPPENING.
IT'S NOT HAPPENING.

91
00:06:09,958 --> 00:06:12,625
- ( screams )
- I KNOW YOU SAW ME, YOU JERK.

92
00:06:12,708 --> 00:06:14,625
- AND YOU FOUND OUT
WHERE I LIVED, HOW?

93
00:06:14,708 --> 00:06:16,083
- WILL AND DETERMINATION.

94
00:06:16,166 --> 00:06:19,000
- AND A LITTLE BIT OF HELP,
THIS IS SO MUCH FUN.

95
00:06:19,083 --> 00:06:21,125
I HELD UP MY END OF THE
BARGAIN, NOW GO AHEAD,

96
00:06:21,208 --> 00:06:23,166
AND BASH IN HER STUPID,
HAPPY FACE.

97
00:06:23,250 --> 00:06:24,500
- DAMN YOU, POVERTY GOD,

98
00:06:24,583 --> 00:06:26,583
I'LL MAKE YOU PAY FOR
SELLING ME OUT LIKE THIS.

99
00:06:26,666 --> 00:06:29,166
- HEY, DON'T BLAME THIS
ON HER! IT'S YOUR FAULT,

100
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:31,250
I CAN'T STAND PEOPLE WHO
DON'T TAKE RESPONSIBILITY

101
00:06:31,333 --> 00:06:32,625
FOR THEIR OWN
ACTIONS AND FESS UP

102
00:06:32,708 --> 00:06:34,083
TO THE AWFUL THINGS
THEY'VE DONE.

103
00:06:34,166 --> 00:06:35,791
YOU'RE NOTHING BUT A BIG COWARD.

104
00:06:35,875 --> 00:06:37,125
- WELL, AT LEAST I
DON'T GO AROUND

105
00:06:37,208 --> 00:06:38,750
BREAKING DOWN PEOPLE'S DOORS.

106
00:06:38,833 --> 00:06:41,833
- YOU FULL BLOWN NUT- JOB.
- A NUT- JOB?

107
00:06:41,916 --> 00:06:44,625
- COME ON, DON'T LET HER
BEAT YOU, SAY SOMETHING.

108
00:06:44,708 --> 00:06:46,208
- WELL, YOUR BOOBS ARE HUGE.

109
00:06:46,291 --> 00:06:48,791
- YOU COULD'VE BEEN A LITTLE
MEANER, BUT GOOD EFFORT.

110
00:06:48,875 --> 00:06:50,250
- ( chuckles )

111
00:06:50,333 --> 00:06:53,291
THAT'S SWEET OF YOU, BUT WAS
THAT REALLY YOUR COMEBACK?

112
00:06:53,375 --> 00:06:55,250
YOU, MAN- FACED TOM- BOY.

113
00:06:55,333 --> 00:06:56,458
- ( screaming )

114
00:06:56,541 --> 00:07:00,500
- SCREW YOU, GAZONGA GIRL.
- UH- OH.

115
00:07:00,583 --> 00:07:02,666
- ( screams )

116
00:07:02,750 --> 00:07:04,666
- MORON, DID SHE ACTUALLY
THINK SHE COULD WIN THE DAY

117
00:07:04,750 --> 00:07:06,333
AGAINST MY HAPPINESS ENERGY?

118
00:07:06,416 --> 00:07:08,208
- 'E', IT'S FOR EFFORT.

119
00:07:08,291 --> 00:07:10,250
- ( exclaims )

120
00:07:10,333 --> 00:07:14,166
- LISTEN UP, LADY PANTS. YOU'LL
PAY FOR THIS, I PROMISE YOU.

121
00:07:14,250 --> 00:07:18,041
IT IS ON LIKE DONKEY KONG.
YOU VERSUS ME, ONE ON ONE.

122
00:07:18,125 --> 00:07:19,416
- WELL, YOU GONNA FIGHT HER?

123
00:07:19,500 --> 00:07:23,916
- SHE FELL THIRTEEN STORIES,
HOW IS SHE STILL ALIVE?

124
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:26,333
- Male Student: ICHIKO'S GONNA
BATTLE THE NEW TRANSFER STUDENT.

125
00:07:26,416 --> 00:07:27,666
- CAT FIGHT!
- CAT FIGHT!

126
00:07:27,750 --> 00:07:29,208
- NOWHERE TO RUN THIS TIME,
IS THERE, COWARD?

127
00:07:29,291 --> 00:07:31,250
- IF ANYBODY SHOULD
BE RUNNING AWAY, IT'S YOU.

128
00:07:35,166 --> 00:07:36,583
- TWO HUNDRED ON ICHIKO.
- RINDO ALL THE WAY.

129
00:07:36,666 --> 00:07:38,708
- COLAS, CANDY, POPCORN,
ICE- COLD BEER!

130
00:07:38,791 --> 00:07:40,458
- DUDE, WE'RE AT SCHOOL,
YOU CAN'T SELL BEER HERE.

131
00:07:40,541 --> 00:07:42,541
- NAH, IT'S COOL, I SAW
OUR TEACHER BUY SOME EARLIER.

132
00:07:42,625 --> 00:07:44,541
- OKAY, THE LOSER OF
THIS MATCH HAS TO DO

133
00:07:44,625 --> 00:07:46,291
WHATEVER THE WINNER
TELLS THEM TO DO.

134
00:07:46,375 --> 00:07:49,041
- THAT'S OKAY BY ME,
JUST BE AWARE, IF I WIN,

135
00:07:49,125 --> 00:07:50,833
I'M GONNA MAKE YOU
LEAVE THIS SCHOOL.

136
00:07:50,916 --> 00:07:53,833
- OH IS THAT SO?
THEN MAY THE BEST GIRL WIN.

137
00:07:56,500 --> 00:07:59,125
I'VE WORKED MY BUTT OFF
TO GET AS STRONG AS I AM.

138
00:07:59,208 --> 00:08:02,625
NO WAY IN HELL, I'LL LET YOU
TAKE THAT AWAY.

139
00:08:02,708 --> 00:08:05,291
I HOPE YOU'RE READY
FOR A BEAT DOWN, LADY PANTS.

140
00:08:05,375 --> 00:08:08,250
'CAUSE GUESS WHAT?
YOU'RE GETTING ONE.

141
00:08:09,750 --> 00:08:12,916
- HMM.

142
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,791
- IT'S THE END OF THE LINE
FOR YOU, GIVE UP RIGHT NOW,

143
00:08:15,875 --> 00:08:18,333
OR FACE MY TERRIBLE WRATH.

144
00:08:18,416 --> 00:08:20,125
LAST CHANCE.

145
00:08:23,708 --> 00:08:24,875
- KILL HER!

146
00:08:24,958 --> 00:08:26,333
- AKANE, YOUR HAIR IS LOOKING
KINDA THROWED.

147
00:08:26,416 --> 00:08:27,583
- SHUT UP!

148
00:08:27,666 --> 00:08:28,750
- ( screams )

149
00:08:29,625 --> 00:08:30,833
- MY EYES.

150
00:08:34,541 --> 00:08:36,083
- DAMN, I'M STUCK.

151
00:08:39,125 --> 00:08:41,916
- OW, OW, YOU WIN.
YOU GOT ME. I GIVE UP, OKAY?

152
00:08:42,000 --> 00:08:44,333
- ( people cheering )
- WOW, I TOTALLY DID IT.

153
00:08:44,416 --> 00:08:46,916
- OH, YEAH, AWESOME. WOO.
- WE LOVE YOU, ICHIKO.

154
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:49,875
- IT'S OVER ALREADY?
THAT'S SO LAME.

155
00:08:49,958 --> 00:08:52,291
- IT WOULD'VE BEEN WAY COOLER
IF THEY FOUGHT TO THE DEATH.

156
00:08:52,375 --> 00:08:53,750
- OR IF THEY WERE NAKED.

157
00:08:55,166 --> 00:08:57,666
- SO, HOW'D WE DO?
- OVER NINE THOUSAND.

158
00:08:57,750 --> 00:08:58,791
- OUTSTANDING.

159
00:09:01,458 --> 00:09:03,916
- WE'RE GONNA BE FILTHY
STINKING RICH. ( laughs )

160
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:07,500
- OH, HECK YEAH.
WE ARE EATING OUT TONIGHT.

161
00:09:07,583 --> 00:09:12,000
- THIS SUCKS, HOW COULD
I LOSE TO THAT LITTLE BRAT?

162
00:09:12,083 --> 00:09:14,041
- YO.

163
00:09:14,125 --> 00:09:16,416
- GREAT FIGHT, REAL GOOD STUFF,

164
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:18,666
YOU GAVE US AN AWESOME
SHOW OUT THERE.

165
00:09:18,750 --> 00:09:21,875
IF YOU EVER DO IT AGAIN, I SURE
HOPE YOU'LL GIVE ME A CALL.

166
00:09:21,958 --> 00:09:24,666
- I'LL BE RICH.
- OH, SURE.

167
00:09:27,333 --> 00:09:30,625
- THANKS SO MUCH, WAIT,
WHAT'S YOUR NAME AGAIN?

168
00:09:30,708 --> 00:09:33,666
- I'M KEITA TSUWABUKI.
- AND MY NAME'S MOMIJI.

169
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:34,791
- NOT YOU.

170
00:09:38,875 --> 00:09:41,125
- SO COOL.
- I HATE TO INTERRUPT.

171
00:09:41,208 --> 00:09:42,708
- ( gasps )
- BUT YOU DO REMEMBER,

172
00:09:42,791 --> 00:09:45,083
WHAT I SAID ABOUT WHAT YOU'D
HAVE TO DO IF YOU LOST, RIGHT?

173
00:09:46,166 --> 00:09:47,416
- YES, I REMEMBER.

174
00:09:49,791 --> 00:09:52,833
A PROMISE IS A PROMISE,
I'LL GET OUT OF YOUR HAIR.

175
00:09:54,333 --> 00:09:57,208
- AND SO, THE TOM- BOY,
KARATE- LOVING,

176
00:09:57,291 --> 00:10:01,333
FREAK- SHOW PSYCHOPATH
VANISHED FROM MY SIGHT FOREVER.

177
00:10:01,416 --> 00:10:02,791
- Teacher: WE HAVE A
NEW TRANSFER STUDENT

178
00:10:02,875 --> 00:10:04,625
THAT I'D LIKE TO INTRODUCE
TO YOU TODAY.

179
00:10:04,708 --> 00:10:06,375
- Ichiko: BUT THEN.
SHE CAME BACK!

180
00:10:07,708 --> 00:10:09,416
- THIS IS MISS RINDO,
SHE TRANSFERRED IN,

181
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:11,166
THEN SHE LEFT,
AND NOW SHE'S BACK.

182
00:10:11,250 --> 00:10:15,333
- I ONLY HAVE ONE PURPOSE HERE.
THAT'S TO DESTROY ICHIKO SAKURA.

183
00:10:15,416 --> 00:10:17,250
- I GUESS I SHOULD'VE BEEN A
LITTLE MORE SPECIFIC

184
00:10:17,333 --> 00:10:18,750
WITH MY REQUEST.

185
00:10:18,833 --> 00:10:20,416
- I'M NOT SURE WHY, BUT I HAVE
A FEELING ME AND THIS GIRL

186
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:22,416
ARE GONNA GET ALONG JUST FINE.

187
00:10:32,708 --> 00:10:35,083
- Man: HIDEBU.
- Man 2: UWARABA.

188
00:10:35,166 --> 00:10:37,625
- Man 3: ABESHI.

189
00:10:37,708 --> 00:10:38,916
- ARE YOU TWO ALL RIGHT?

190
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:41,875
- WE'RE FINE, THANK YOU SO
MUCH FOR SAVING US.

191
00:10:41,958 --> 00:10:45,125
- DAMN, THESE PUNKS
ARE NO CHALLENGE AT ALL.

192
00:10:45,208 --> 00:10:48,375
- ICHIKO, I'LL GET YOU
IF IT'S THE LAST THING I DO.

193
00:10:50,375 --> 00:10:51,458
- ( chuckles )

194
00:10:58,166 --> 00:11:00,666
- HERE'S THE DEAL, I WANT
YOU TO FIGHT ME AGAIN.

195
00:11:00,750 --> 00:11:02,416
- WHAT? NO.

196
00:11:04,875 --> 00:11:06,333
- THIS ISN'T AN OPTION, LADY.

197
00:11:06,416 --> 00:11:08,333
YOU AND I ARE GONNA
DO THIS THING.

198
00:11:08,416 --> 00:11:09,833
- WHAT'S YOUR DEAL?

199
00:11:09,916 --> 00:11:12,291
WHAT IS IT ABOUT ME THAT YOU
DON'T LIKE SO MUCH, ANYWAY?

200
00:11:12,375 --> 00:11:14,208
- JUST STOP RIGHT THERE.

201
00:11:14,291 --> 00:11:16,291
- YOU DON'T KNOW WHEN TO QUIT,
DO YOU MISS RINDO?

202
00:11:16,375 --> 00:11:18,791
- WE WON'T LET YOU LAY
ANOTHER HAND ON HER.

203
00:11:18,875 --> 00:11:19,958
- WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU,

204
00:11:20,041 --> 00:11:21,750
WHY ARE YOU SO FREAKING
OBSESSED WITH HER?

205
00:11:21,833 --> 00:11:24,291
- COME ON RANMARU,
TAKE THEM ALL ON AT ONCE.

206
00:11:24,375 --> 00:11:26,666
- HEY, SHUT UP. EVERYBODY
BACK OFF ME RIGHT NOW.

207
00:11:26,750 --> 00:11:28,708
- ALL RIGHT. YOU KIDS
JUST CALM DOWN...

208
00:11:28,791 --> 00:11:30,291
- STOP THIS NONSENSE AT ONCE.

209
00:11:30,375 --> 00:11:33,041
ANY FURTHER CONFRONTATION
WOULD BE POINTLESS.

210
00:11:35,125 --> 00:11:37,791
- BUT, DON'T YOU WORRY,
A REMATCH IS COMING SOON.

211
00:11:37,875 --> 00:11:39,125
- ( students cheering )

212
00:11:40,208 --> 00:11:42,375
- AW, COME ON.
- OH, HELL YEAH.

213
00:11:42,458 --> 00:11:44,416
- YOU DON'T GET TO DECIDE
FOR BOTH OF US.

214
00:11:44,500 --> 00:11:45,416
- GET YOUR TICKETS RIGHT HERE.

215
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:47,416
